# Smart City — Dataset, Failure Analytics & Drift Detection

## Phase 1: Publishable Dataset Collection Pipeline
- [ ] Data collector — automated image scraper with rich metadata
- [ ] Multi-modal enrichment — weather, taxi, air quality per snapshot
- [ ] Dataset formatter — YOLO annotation pipeline + Kaggle-ready packaging
- [ ] Dataset documentation — datacard, statistics, EDA notebook

## Phase 2: Failure Analytics
- [ ] Failure taxonomy — define and classify detection failure modes
- [ ] Failure analysis pipeline — automated detection of failure cases
- [ ] Failure report generator — per-camera and per-condition reporting

## Phase 3: Model Drift Detection
- [ ] Drift monitor — statistical drift detection on predictions over time
- [ ] Drift dashboard metrics — confidence, class distribution, detection count tracking
- [ ] Automated alerts — threshold-based drift alerting with root cause hints

## Phase 4: Integration & Packaging
- [ ] End-to-end config — YAML-driven pipeline configuration
- [ ] README & docs update — reflect new capabilities
- [ ] Kaggle dataset card — metadata, citation, license for publishing
